cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.IR 

The paper focuses on the development of AI-based automated CT image analysis tools for detection, quantification, and tracking of Coronavirus. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions the use of deep learning models, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with medical imaging and disease monitoring, which could place it in cs.MED (Medical Imaging) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
